snippet.title: Jelly Car -- demo of XNA Creators Club game for Xbox 360
snippet.description:
Currently about seven demos of XNA games are available from Xbox Live.  Sorry to say, the demos can only be used until the middle of March 2008.  Well, hopefully the games will become Xbox Live Arcade games.

By far my favorite is Jelly Car :D

The first track I have in this (edited) video I am just showing off some of what the Jelly Car can do.  On the second track I am trying to finish quickly, and doing a so-so job of it.  The third track I was playing with a glitch in the pre-release demo.
